net.proteusframework.users.model

Class Role

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.users.model.Role
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Entity<Long>, LocalizedNamedObject, NamedObject, Auditable, FullyAuditable, PrincipalAuditable, TimeAuditable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Principal

    @Entity
public class Role
extends Object
implements Entity<Long>, LocalizedNamedObject, Serializable, FullyAuditable
    A role encompasses certain permissions and other authorities. Roles can contain other roles, in which case the privileges entitled to the contained role are granted to the containing role.
    Author:
    Ken Logan (ken@i2rd.com)
    See Also:
    Serialized Form

        public void setSessionTimeout(Integer sessionTimeout)
